---

<section id="about" class="py-28 px-6 relative">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section label -->
    <div class="section-label" data-animate>
      <span class="section-number">01</span>
      <span class="section-line"></span>
      <span class="section-label-text">About</span>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-16 items-start mt-4">
      <!-- Text -->
      <div class="md:col-span-3 space-y-5" data-animate data-delay="100">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold leading-tight">
          Building products at the <span class="gradient-text">intersection of hardware and software</span>.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed text-lg">
          I'm a Nepali-American product leader and engineer with over a decade of experience 
          spanning energy technology, climate tech, and autonomous robotics. From designing 
          hybrid drill bits at Baker Hughes to leading product for next-gen automation systems 
          at Orbex Group — I've always been drawn to complex, technical problems.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed text-lg">
          At Orbex, I wear many hats. Product strategy, marketing, business analysis — 
          whatever it takes to help a growing company scale. I'm implementing the systems 
          and processes (CRM, analytics, go-to-market) that turn a good product into a 
          sustainable business.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed text-lg">
          Off the clock, I'm a tinkerer. I build SaaS tools, experiment with AI agent systems, 
          and chase side projects that keep the engineering muscle sharp. The best product leaders 
          are the ones who can also ship.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Photo + stats -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2 flex flex-col items-center gap-8" data-animate data-delay="200">
        <!-- Photo -->
        <div class="relative w-56 h-56">
          <div class="photo-glow"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-2 border-border z-10">
            <img 
              src="/images/bibek.jpg" 
              alt="Bibek Ghimire" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <!-- Rotating decoration -->
          <svg class="absolute inset-[-12px] w-[calc(100%+24px)] h-[calc(100%+24px)]" viewBox="0 0 200 200">
            <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="96" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="4 6" style="animation: rotate 20s linear infinite;" />
          </svg>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 w-full">
          <div class="text-center">
            <span class="stat-number" data-count="13" data-suffix="+">0</span>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">Years Exp.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <span class="stat-number" data-count="3">0</span>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">Industries</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <span class="stat-number" data-count="2">0</span>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">Degrees</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Quick facts card -->
        <div class="bg-bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-5 w-full space-y-3">
          <div>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-xs uppercase tracking-wider font-mono">Education</p>
            <p class="text-text-primary text-sm font-medium mt-1">B.S. Aerospace & Mechanical Engineering</p>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-xs">Oklahoma State University</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-t border-border pt-3">
            <p class="text-text-muted text-xs uppercase tracking-wider font-mono">Philosophy</p>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm italic mt-1">
              "Lead through influence, strive for better, continuously learn."
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
